text: "Impossible" is a song recorded by Swedish singer Måns Zelmerlöw. It was released on 16 November 2009 as a digital download in Sweden. It was released as the third single from his second studio album MZW (2009). The song was written by Aleena Gibson, Måns Zelmerlöw and Dan Sandquist.
